beer.beer_description:
Better red than dead we reckon, which is why we’ve packed this Red IPA fit to burst with Mosaic and Citra hops woven around a full, malty base. An AIBA Gold Medal-winning beer, it’s a flavourful yet well-balanced and aromatic brew that’s just the thing for a mellow night around the fire with your besties chatting about, you know, stuff.
Unfiltered, Unpasteurised, No Preservatives.
